Let it Ride (05/04/2026)

Players pass a solo cup around, each attempting to bounce a ping pong ball into it.
    *If a player makes it they can either put a quarter in the cup or recieve an anti-quarter.
     If a player misses, they take X amount of drinks, where X is the number of quarters in the cup.
   
*An anti-quarter allows you to remove a quarter from the cup.(Can only use on your turn)

If a player recieves a cup with 4 quarters in it, and end their turn with 4 quarters in the cup. Then they automatically loose.

Once a player recieves 7 cups they win and recieve 1 pt. Players continue unitl a loose is determined.
Loser is the last player to get 7 cups.

Loser gives 1 point to the winner.